formula: Continued fraction expansion: BesselJ(0,2) = 1/(4 + 4/(8 + 9/(15 + ... + (n - 1)^2/(n^2 + 1 + ...)))). See A073701 for a proof. - _Peter Bala_, Feb 01 2015
